  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The transport left on June 30, and who would participate and who would not participate was uncertain up to the last moment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But tragedy happened in our family on June 14.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On June 14, the-- in accordance with the family council, in which I did not participate, but about which I was informed, the heads of the families, meaning my grandparents, the six brothers, and the sister, got together and decided that they will risk-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they will risk a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a-- a venture into Romania, to escape to Romania.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the council determined that two of the six brothers and their families should take advantage of this offer, which was obtained through the SS, through an SS authority.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The idea was that the SS truck would come and would pick them up at their home and would take them to Romania, deliver them to Romania, against the payment of certain amounts.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And upon return, there would be a letter from the people who, by that time, would be in Romania, and that these people would then be-- the-- the SS people-- would then be-- then be instructed to deliver the letter to the rest of the family, and the rest of the family would make the second payment.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So two of my uncles, each of them with-- with his wife and two children, were collected by the SS and were on their way to Romania.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What the SS people didn't-- and were paid-- the SS people were paid partly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What the SS people didn't know was that the code was arranged between the remaining members of the family.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
